<a name="Cinema影院类"></a>
## Cinema 影院类
<a name="根据id获取影院详情"></a>
### 根据id获取影院详情
Request URI
```
GET /api/cinemas/{id}
```
Response Format
```
{
	"id":String,
	"name":String,
	"address":String,
	"phone":String,
	"cityName":String
}
```
