<a name="根据电影id获取电影演出列表"></a>
### 根据电影id获取电影演出列表
Request URI
```
GET /api/showings/movie/{movieId}
```
**返回今天和明天两天的排期**
Response Format
```
{
    "size": Integer,
    "showinglist": [
        {
            "date": String, //今天
            "cinemaList": [
				{
				"id":String,
				"name":String
				},
				{
				"id":String, 
				"name":String
				}
			]
        },
		{
            "date": String, //明天
            "cinemaList": [
				{
				"id":String,
				"name":String
				},
				{
				"id":String, 
				"name":String
				}
			]
        }
    ]
}
```
